      "lineNbr": 101,
      "author": {
        "id": 1001314
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-02-19T12:48:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Both Overview and Power need the same semantics (checkbox \u003d power cap on/off, input \u003d SetPoint, synced from server). Keeping the form model in the composable (with the existing watch that syncs server → form) means one place owns that behavior; moving it to the view would duplicate sync and semantics in every consumer.",
      "parentUuid": "cf39464d_e8f08806",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 88,
        "startChar": 2,
        "endLine": 101,
        "endChar": 4
      },
